thread.title: Zack Yusof
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Zack Yusof

author: Zack Yusof
title: Zack Yusof
text: Went to buy a pair of studio monitors at Store DJ's Perth branch in Carrington. What i encountered was friendly service, knowledgable staff and a really comprehensive selection of gear. It was my first time shopping at Store DJ and I was not dissapointed in the slightest. Would i recommend the company to people? Most definitely.
